headline: Teradyne’s AI Test And Robotics Push Fuels Debate On Rich Valuation
summary: Teradyne, NasdaqGS:TER, has formed a joint venture with MultiLane to develop high speed test solutions for AI data centers. The company is also reporting significant growth in its Robotics segment tied to AI use in e commerce and logistics. These moves highlight Teradyne's broader role in AI infrastructure and automation markets.
